᱒᱕ ᱮᱯᱨᱤᱞ ᱒᱐᱑᱕ ᱥᱟᱞᱮ ᱱᱮᱯᱟᱞ ᱨᱮ ᱦᱩᱭ ᱞᱮᱱ ᱚᱛᱞᱟᱲᱟᱣ (earthquake) ᱨᱮ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱦᱚᱱᱚᱛ (ᱡᱤᱞᱟᱹ) ᱦᱚᱸ ᱚᱨᱥᱚᱝ ᱞᱮᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref>{{cite news|title=Nepal family finds starting over tough in wake of earthquake|url=http://www.nwitimes.com/news/local/porter/nepal-family-finds-starting-over-tough-in-wake-of-earthquake/article_fdbfe121-eed1-5762-a684-eb4036628403.html|accessdate=21 June 2015|agency=[http://www.nwitimes.com The Times]|publisher=nwi.com|date=13 June 2015|ref=www.nwitimes.com}}</ref>



